Dream collab between @midnightcosm and @hotdogpets.co!

Last year, the two brands came together to create a limited-edition mist for dogs. Existing in opposite visual worlds —Midnight is minimal and sophisticated, while HotDog is expressive and irreverent— the challenge was not only to come up with something exciting, but to equally portray both universes in an unexpected yet seamless way.

The mist is designed to hydrate, soften, and refresh the dog’s fur. These qualities are often expressed through movement — showing the hair flowing freely in the air.

With this in mind, we created a series of illustrations featuring different dogs with expressive, joyful faces and beautifully flowing hair, visually capturing the product’s effect.

In juxtaposition with Midnight’s simple black-and-white packaging, this intervention helped us preserve and celebrate the DNA of both brands: Midnight provides the structure; HotDog brings the emotion.

